K10D0279_H0281:130b-1: a'arya buddha aa nu smri ti /
K10D0279_H0281:130b-3: 'phags pa sangs rgyas rjes su dran pa /
K10D0279_H0281:130b-5: byang chub sems dpa' thams cad la phyag 'tshal lo //
K10D0279_H0281:130b-6: 'di ltar sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das de ni de
K10D0279_H0281:130b-7: bzhin gshegs pa dgra bcom pa yang dag par rdzogs
K10D0279_H0281:130b-8: pa'i sangs rgyas / rig pa dang /
K10D0279_H0281:130b-12: skyes bu 'dul ba'i kha lo sgyur ba bla na med pa /
K10D0279_H0281:130b-13: lha dang mi rnams kyi ston pa /
K10D0279_H0281:130b-15: de bzhin gshegs pa de dag ni bsod nams dag gi rgyu mthun pa /
K10D0279_H0281:130b-16: dge ba'i rtsa ba rnams chud mi za ba /
K10D0279_H0281:130b-18: bsod nams kyi gter rnams kyi gzhi /
K10D0279_H0281:130b-19: dpe byad bzang po rnams kyis spras pa /
K10D0279_H0281:130b-20: mtshan rnams kyi me tog rgyas pa /
K10D0279_H0281:130b-21: spyod yul ran par mthun pa /
K10D0279_H0281:130b-22: mthong na mi mthun pa med pa /
K10D0279_H0281:130b-23: dad pas mos pa rnams mngon par dga' ba /
K10D0279_H0281:130b-24: shes rab zil gyis mi non pa /
K10D0279_H0281:130b-25: stobs rnams la brdzi ba med pa /
K10D0279_H0281:130b-26: sems can thams cad kyi ston pa /
K10D0279_H0281:130b-27: byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyi yab /
K10D0279_H0281:130b-28: 'phags pa'i gang zag rnams kyi rgyal po /
K10D0279_H0281:130b-29: mya ngan las 'das pa'i grong khyer du 'gro ba rnams kyi ded dpon /
K10D0279_H0281:130b-30: ye shes dpag tu med pa /
K10D0279_H0281:130b-31: spobs pa bsam gyis mi khyab pa /
K10D0279_H0281:130b-34: sku byad lta bas chog mi shes pa /
K10D0279_H0281:131a-2: 'dod pa dag gis ma gos pa /
K10D0279_H0281:131a-3: gzugs dag gis nye bar ma gos pa /
K10D0279_H0281:131a-4: gzugs med pa dag dang ma 'dres pa /
K10D0279_H0281:131a-5: sdug bsngal las rnam par grol ba phung po dag las rab tu rnam par grol pa /
K10D0279_H0281:131a-6: khams rnams dang mi ldan pa /
K10D0279_H0281:131a-8: mdud pa rnams shin tu bcad pa /
K10D0279_H0281:131a-9: yongs su gdung ba dag las rnam par grol ba /
K10D0279_H0281:131a-10: sred pa las shin tu grol ba /
K10D0279_H0281:131a-12: ye shes yongs su rdzogs pa /
K10D0279_H0281:131a-15: da ltar byung ba'i sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das rnams kyi ye shes la gnas pa /
K10D0279_H0281:131a-16: mya ngan las 'das pa la mi gnas pa /
K10D0279_H0281:131a-17: yang dag pa nyid kyi mtha' la gnas pa /
K10D0279_H0281:131a-18: sems can thams cad la gzigs pa'i sa la bzhugs pa ste /
K10D0279_H0281:131a-19: 'di dag ni de bzhin gshegs pa'i ye shes yang dag pa'i che ba'i yon tan yin no //
